skdetail:

Invocation Name: bruh sound effect
des:
The long-awaited "bruh" sound effect is now here, also known as "Bruh Sound Effect #2". This meme has recently been popularized, as its versatility is unique from all other memes. Bring up this effect at any time for a fitting reaction to any confusing and disappointing situations.

Your homie just spilled his oatmeal over your new kicks? 
"Alexa, open Bruh Sound Effect."

You wake up to find that the dog tore up your couch, but you don't have a dog?
"Alexa, open Bruh Sound Effect."

You've just flushed the toilet and the water starts to rise?
"Alexa, open Bruh Sound Effect."

Pull up your favorite sound effect anytime, anywhere.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
